dc_creator_sm: Department of Public Works and Department of Public Affairs
dc_description_s: San Francisco Neighborhoods as designated by the San Francisco Association of Realtors (SFAR).  The data set was digitized from paper maps provided by Public Affairs personnel. DPW/ Public Affairs drew boundaries and assigned designations to 88 distinct neighborhoods. Note: Chinatown is not  designated.
dc_publisher_s: San Francisco (Calif.). Department Of Telecommunications and Information Services.
dc_title_s: San Francisco Neighborhoods (Designated by SF Assoc. of Realtors)
